description_html: The Cityscape dining table by Artistica Home is a contemporary asymmetrical design crafted from stainless steel. Certain elements are electroformed with brass in a vintage coloration, creating a striking multi-tone appearance. The base is paired with a 60-inch glass top. This table makes an excellent entry or statement piece. Dimensions: 60W x 60D x 30.25H in. Diameter: 60 in.
product_name: Cityscape Dining Table by Artistica Home
